graph TD
A(open native camera app <br> or qr code scanner)-->B[/hold phone displaying 'connect code'<br> in camera's viewfinder/]
B-->C[a notification pops up<br>prompting the user to tap]
C-->D[/tapping the notification/]
C-->1[/dismiss notification/]
1-->2(notification dismisses)
D-->E[brings up the, in the 'connect code'<br>encoded, contact info<br>as an overlay view]
E-->F{save or cancel}
F-->G[/save/]
F-->H[/cancel/]
H-->I(contact info overlay view dismisses)
G-->J[contact saved<br>to phone contacts app]
J-->K(contact info overlay view dismisses)
classDef def fill: #000, stroke: #709, color: #fff, path: #fff, edge: #fff
class 0,A,B,C,D,E,F,G,H,I,J,K,L,M,N def
